pec","bio":null,"image":"https://conduit-api.bondaracademy.com/images/smiley-cyrus.jpeg","following":false}},{"slug":"Cotter-Pyke-51031","title":"Cotter Pyke","description":"Old Ghis","body":"Summer will end soon enough, and childhood as well.","tagList":["Wendwater"],"createdAt":"2026-04-08T21:56:46.393Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-08T21:56:46.393Z","favorited":false,"favoritesCount":0,"author":{"username":"jesusdquispec","bio":null,"image":"https://conduit-api.bondaracademy.com/images/smiley-cyrus.jpeg","following":false}},{"slug":"Catelyn-Stark-51031","title":"Catelyn Stark","description":"Meereen","body":"Do the dead frighten you?","tagList":["Meadows of Grassy Vale"],"createdAt":"2026-04-08T21:54:59.254Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-08T21:54:59.254Z","favorited":false,"favoritesCount":0,"author":{"username":"jesusdquispec","bio":null,"image":"https://conduit-api.bondaracademy.com/images/smiley-cyrus.jpeg","following":false}},{"slug":"Haggon-51031","title":"Haggon","description":"New Ghis","body":"Winter is coming.","tagList":["Connington of Griffin's Roost"],"createdAt":"2026-04-08T21:47:28.696Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-08T21:47:28.696Z","favorited":false,"favoritesCount":0,"author":{"username":"jesusdquispec","bio":null,"image":"https://conduit-api.bondaracademy.com/images/smiley-cyrus.jpeg","following":false}},{"slug":"Sargon-Botley-51031","title":"Sargon Botley","description":"Ar Noy","body":"When the snows fall and the white winds blow, the lone wolf dies but the pack survives.","tagList":["Peake of Starpike"],"createdAt":"2026-04-08T21:33:03.530Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-08T21:33:03.530Z","favorited":false,"favoritesCount":0,"author":{"username":"jesusdquispec","bio":null,"image":"https://conduit-api.bondaracademy.com/images/smiley-cyrus.jpeg","following":false}},{"slug":"Ghost-of-High-Heart-51031","title":"Ghost of High Heart","description":"King's Landing","body":"The things I do for love.","tagList":["Fowler of Skyreach"],"createdAt":"2026-04-07T06:48:04.236Z","updatedAt"